sequenceDiagram
    participant Orchestrator as FMS Guardrails<br/>Orchestrator
    participant Detector as Guardrails Regex Detector<br/>8080/TCP HTTP

    Note over Orchestrator,Detector: Flow 1: Health Check
    Orchestrator->>Detector: GET /health<br/>HTTP 8080/TCP<br/>No Auth
    Detector-->>Orchestrator: 200 OK "healthy"

    Note over Orchestrator,Detector: Flow 2: Built-in PII Detection (e.g. email)
    Orchestrator->>Detector: POST /api/v1/text/contents<br/>HTTP 8080/TCP<br/>No Auth<br/>{"contents": ["text..."],<br/>"detector_params": {"regex": ["email"]}}
    Note right of Detector: Matches built-in email pattern<br/>against input text
    Detector-->>Orchestrator: 200 OK<br/>[{"start": N, "end": M,<br/>"text": "user@example.com",<br/>"detection_type": "email",<br/>"detection": "email",<br/>"score": 1.0}]

    Note over Orchestrator,Detector: Flow 3: Custom Regex Detection
    Orchestrator->>Detector: POST /api/v1/text/contents<br/>HTTP 8080/TCP<br/>No Auth<br/>{"contents": ["text..."],<br/>"detector_params": {"regex": ["\\d{3}-\\d{4}"]}}
    Note right of Detector: Compiles and applies<br/>custom regex pattern
    Detector-->>Orchestrator: 200 OK<br/>[{"start": N, "end": M,<br/>"text": "555-1234",<br/>"detection_type": "custom_regex",<br/>"detection": "\\d{3}-\\d{4}",<br/>"score": 1.0}]

    Note over Orchestrator,Detector: Flow 4: Multiple Built-in Patterns (ssn, credit-card)
    Orchestrator->>Detector: POST /api/v1/text/contents<br/>HTTP 8080/TCP<br/>{"contents": ["text..."],<br/>"detector_params": {"regex": ["ssn", "credit-card"]}}
    Note right of Detector: Runs SSN and credit card<br/>regex patterns against input
    Detector-->>Orchestrator: 200 OK<br/>[{...ssn match...}, {...cc match...}]
